<h3 class="jTitle">Day Zero &#8211; The Search For PERFECT Skin Begins!</h3>
<p>Ok everyone &#8211; even though I have done this so many times before &#8211; I&#8217;m going to give it another try! I&#8217;m on the hunt for a face cream that will FINALLY get rid of my lines, wrinkles and blemishes &#8211; and give me flawless movie star skin. I hope this search (and this blog) are my last (LOL)&#8230; with so many failures in the past, it&#8217;s hard to be optimistic. So everyone can follow my progress &#8211; here is a picture of how I look right now &#8211; as I start my search for a new cream. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-111 size-full" src="<?= $assets ?>/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/1-IMG_8312-modified.jpg" alt="Betty" width="480" height="640" /></p>
