<p><i>Angelina Jolie always manages to look radiant on the red carpet.</i></p>
<p>And it turns out that when it comes to maintaining her looks, the actress has yet another trick up her sleeve &#8211; regular high-tech facials from Hollywood&#8217;s top skin doctor, at a cost of $25,000 a year&#8230; The 39-year-old actress met the doctor four years ago on the set of a Russian spy thriller, and since then is believed to have spent (Over $100,000 in just four years on skin treatments)!</p>
<p><b>US DOCTOR Recommends TWO CREAMS for FLAWLESS SKIN:</b></p>
